attributes.mlflow.spanInputs: {"prompt": "Generate Cisco IOS XR 7.0.1 telemetry configuration for LACP/EtherChannel operational monitoring (bundles, members, counters). Use gRPC with no TLS. Telemetry server is 192.0.2.118 on port 57500. Choose relevant sensor-paths."}
attributes.mlflow.spanOutputs:
"telemetry model-driven
 sensor-group LACP-OPERATIONAL
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-ifmgr-oper:bundle-interfaces/bundle-interface
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-ifmgr-oper:bundle-interface-members/bundle-interface-member
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-ifmgr-oper:bundle-interface-counters/bundle-interface-counter
 !
 destination-group DG-GRPC
  address-family ipv4
   destination 192.0.2.118
    port 57500
    encoding self-describing-gpb
    protocol grpc no-tls
 !
 subscription SUB-LACP-OPERATIONAL
  sensor-group-id LACP-OPERATIONAL sample-interval 30000
  destination-group-id DG-GRPC
 !"
